parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates forward without input from the driver
even when the brakes are applied
and may not respond to attempts to shift into park or neutral.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause a loud noise, distraction, and potentially lead to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: The sunroof explodes or shatters without any apparent cause
often while the vehicle is in motion
and may continue to crack or shatter even after the vehicle has stopped.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the radio navigation system can cause distraction, inconvenience, and potentially lead to accidents if the driver is not paying attention to the road.
symptoms: The radio navigation system turns off and resets for no apparent reason
causing the loss of navigation data and requiring the driver to re-input their destination.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Frayed Airbag Wires and Harness Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag wires and harness can prevent the airbags from deploying in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: Airbag light comes on
airbags fail to deploy in a crash
wires under the driver's seat are frayed
harness needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed Recall Repair for Airbag Issue
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in recall repair for the airbag issue can lead to a prolonged period of increased risk of injury or fatality due to non-deployment of airbags in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Notification of recall
but parts are not available
dealer is unable to perform repair
manufacturer exceeds reasonable time for recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure of Airbags to Deploy in a Crash
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality to the occupants.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
vehicle is damaged
occupants are injured
recall notice is received after the incident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The uncomfortable headrests can cause discomfort, pain, and poor posture, leading to chronic neck and back pain.
symptoms: Headrests push the head and neck forward
causing discomfort
pain
and poor posture.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's seat can cause injuries, including back injuries, in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The driver's seat moves forward and backward into the rear seats
potentially causing injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Takata Recall - Driver Seat Frame Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver seat frame can cause injuries, including back injuries, in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The driver seat frame needs to be replaced
potentially causing injuries if not addressed.
